//    Description:      This example will show all how to lift the Arm to a specific 
//                      position and hold that position.  Next, lower the arm and hold 
//                      that position.  Stop the motor at the end of the program so that
//                      the Arm returns to its original position.
//    Brain Supported:  1st generation           
//    Configuration:    ArmMotor in Port 10                  
//                                                                            
