//                       TouchLED depending on which way the BaseBot is tilted.
//    Brain Supported:   2nd generation
//    Configuration:     BaseBot (Drivetrain 2-motor, Inertial)
//                       Left Motor in Port 1
//                       Right Motor in Port 6
//                       TouchLED in Port 2
